sentence: Wyoming Rep. Liz Cheney, who in recent years has emerged as the Harley Quinn of Washington's Never Trump suicide squad, is facing a tough reelection fight against Harriet Hageman, a former Cheney adviser who has since been Trump-pilled.
title: The Democrats' complicated dance with neoconservative heiress Liz Cheney
